    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "Organizer c. A. Young of the\nAmerican Federation of Labor will\nprobably be in Spokane in the near\nfuture. At the meeting of the Falls\nCity Trades and Labor assembly, held\nlast evening. letter was received\nfro mthe headquarters of the Ameri-\ncan Federation stating that Mr..\nYoung was in Walla Walla, and If\nthe assembly deemed 1t advisable Mr..\nYoung would be sent to Spokane. The\nsecretary was instructed to tele-\ngraph Frank Morrison, secretary of\nthe American Federation of Labor,\nto have Mr.. Young come on to Spo-\nkane."
    }
  ]
